LOOKING FOR LARGEST FILES OR FOLDERS

## SHOW FIRST 10 LARGEST FILES ##

Get-ChildItem -Path G:\ -Recurse -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Sort-Object Length -Descending | Select-Object -First 10


## SHOW FIRST 10 LARGEST FOLDERS ##

Get-ChildItem C:\ -Recurse -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Sort-Object Length -Descending | Select-Object -First 10
